com.djrapitops.plan.addons.placeholderapi.placeholders

Class AbstractPlanPlaceHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djrapitops.plan.addons.placeholderapi.placeholders.AbstractPlanPlaceHolder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OperatorPlaceholders, PlayerPlaceHolder, ServerPlaceHolders, SessionPlaceHolder, WorldTimePlaceHolder

    public abstract class AbstractPlanPlaceHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    abstract class used for plan placeholders list. This class contains most used methods (static methods and non-static one). It is also used as a universe interface for the Plan-placeholders instances onPlaceholderRequest(Player, String). Check PlanPlaceHolders to learn more how it is used.
    See Also:
    PlanPlaceHolders

      • onPlaceholderRequest

        public abstract java.lang.String onPlaceholderRequest(org.bukkit.entity.Player p,
                                                      java.lang.String params)
                                               throws java.lang.Exception
        Look up the placeholder and check if it is registered in this instance.
        Parameters:
        p - the player who is viewing the placeholder
        params - the placeholder to look up to.
        Returns:
        the value of the placeholder if found, or empty String if no value found but the placeholder is registered, otherwise null
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - if any error occurs
